  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Tough Nut to Crack</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goetz is a challenging game. But if you have a soft spot for planning ahead and making your units help each other to create a choreography that will bring the enemies to their knees, Goetz is for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/ddda9ea1f31b84f34b7ef6cdb217e555.poster.avif?t=1735890259\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/ddda9ea1f31b84f34b7ef6cdb217e555.webm?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/ddda9ea1f31b84f34b7ef6cdb217e555.mp4?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Every Picture Tells a Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each solved mission is accompanied by a rewarding narrative piece, lovingly illustrated and fully voiced by a cast of over 12 voice-over artists. These not only seamlessly tie into the gameplay, but will draw you into a captivating story of friendship and intrigue that never takes itself too seriously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/43a57e5f490cc253023194710ac59986.poster.avif?t=1735890259\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/43a57e5f490cc253023194710ac59986.webm?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/43a57e5f490cc253023194710ac59986.mp4?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Thing of the Past</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A faithful rendering of a 15th century medieval Europe awaits you. Step by step uncover the detailed world map from clandestine woods to icy mountains, delve into the original music and unlock bonus missions off the beaten path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/f68e15158b7653721712daa97dff738a.poster.avif?t=1735890259\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/f68e15158b7653721712daa97dff738a.webm?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/f68e15158b7653721712daa97dff738a.mp4?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Only Time will Tell</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goetz is not a casual experience. It is designed to accompany you on long train rides or give you a good time on a rainy evening. Let yourself sink into the puzzles and you will be rewarded with beautiful solutions and round about 8 hours of unique content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/cc509b461502e174cb47bd0996d286e3.poster.avif?t=1735890259\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/cc509b461502e174cb47bd0996d286e3.webm?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/cc509b461502e174cb47bd0996d286e3.mp4?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Tough Nut to Crack</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goetz is a challenging game. But if you have a soft spot for planning ahead and making your units help each other to create a choreography that will bring the enemies to their knees, Goetz is for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/ddda9ea1f31b84f34b7ef6cdb217e555.poster.avif?t=1735890259\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/ddda9ea1f31b84f34b7ef6cdb217e555.webm?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/ddda9ea1f31b84f34b7ef6cdb217e555.mp4?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Every Picture Tells a Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each solved mission is accompanied by a rewarding narrative piece, lovingly illustrated and fully voiced by a cast of over 12 voice-over artists. These not only seamlessly tie into the gameplay, but will draw you into a captivating story of friendship and intrigue that never takes itself too seriously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/43a57e5f490cc253023194710ac59986.poster.avif?t=1735890259\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/43a57e5f490cc253023194710ac59986.webm?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/43a57e5f490cc253023194710ac59986.mp4?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Thing of the Past</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A faithful rendering of a 15th century medieval Europe awaits you. Step by step uncover the detailed world map from clandestine woods to icy mountains, delve into the original music and unlock bonus missions off the beaten path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/f68e15158b7653721712daa97dff738a.poster.avif?t=1735890259\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/f68e15158b7653721712daa97dff738a.webm?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/f68e15158b7653721712daa97dff738a.mp4?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Only Time will Tell</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goetz is not a casual experience. It is designed to accompany you on long train rides or give you a good time on a rainy evening. Let yourself sink into the puzzles and you will be rewarded with beautiful solutions and round about 8 hours of unique content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/cc509b461502e174cb47bd0996d286e3.poster.avif?t=1735890259\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/cc509b461502e174cb47bd0996d286e3.webm?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3391930/extras/cc509b461502e174cb47bd0996d286e3.mp4?t=1735890259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
